title: [Classic] Corps brulants (1976)
description:
Corps Brulants (1976)



Catherine Ringer [LezOnly]

Chantal Fourquet

Daniele Troeger (as Danielle Stranger)

Michele Perello 


Although he already has a gorgeous similar-aged girlfriend, a teenage boy falls in love with a somewhat older lady, and develops an intimacy with her while she is feeling lonesome with her live-in lover's being away. When the man eventually returns to the lady's house and the boy sees them making love, the boy is initially heartbroken, but then he realizes that his own cute teenage girlfriend is better suited to him, anyway
